</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="15.[125,1172,891,947]" pageId="15" pageNumber="278">
broadened at middle (
<figureCitation box="[390,518,891,915]" captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="15.[169,229,797,816]" captionTargetBox="[170,1128,133,761]" captionTargetId="figure-206@15.[170,1128,133,761]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="Figure 5. Amiota (Amiota) curvispina Chen and Gao, sp. nov. „ (see Figure 4 for further explanation)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4657907" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4657907/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="278">Figure 5C</figureCitation>
